.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-4::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, jazz, disco, classical
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, subway, train, trike
1. the fan disco is on the left of the fan classical##1
2. the fan jazz is somewhere to the left of the person driving the quad-bike##5
3. the person driving the trike is not the fan jazz##6
4. the person driving the trike is somewhere to the right of the person driving the quad-bike##5
5. the person driving the train is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
6. the fan classical is somewhere to the left of the person driving the trike##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |    4     |
| Pet         | jazz | disco | classical     | blues |
| Transport   | subway     | train    | quad-bike | trike    |

