.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, mystery, spy, thriller
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, alhambra, aristoff, dunhill
1. the tiparillo-smoker is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
2. the person watching thriller movies is not the alhambra-smoker##6
3. the tiparillo-smoker is on the far right##1
4. the alhambra-smoker is somewhere to the right of the dunhill-smoker##5
5. the person watching spy movies is the person watching spy movies##1
6. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the left of the tiparillo-smoker##5
7. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching disaster movies##5
8. the person watching mystery movies is somewhere to the left of the dunhill-smoker##5
9. the person watching mystery movies is somewhere to the left of the dunhill-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | spy    | disaster  | thriller   |
| Nationality   | aristoff  | dunhill | alhambra | tiparillo |

