The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, journalist, photographer, social-worker
1. the coach is on the left of the journalist##1
2. the social-worker is somewhere to the left of the photographer##5
3. the social-worker is on the right of the journalist##1
4. the journalist is on the left or right of the person playing snooker##3
5. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left or right of the journalist##3
6. the coach is on the left or right of the person playing go##3
7. the person playing scrabble is somewhere to the right of the person playing mah-jongg##5
8. the person playing snooker is not the social-worker##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Beverage   | snooker  | go        | mah-jongg      | scrabble          |
| Job        | coach | journalist | social-worker | photographer |

