.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, fisherman, lawyer, teacher
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, june, march, july
1. the bartender is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in june is not the teacher##6
3. the person who's birthday is in november is somewhere to the right of the lawyer##5
4. the person who's birthday is in july is in an even position##4
5. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
6. the person who's birthday is in july is the lawyer##1
7. the bartender is not the person who's birthday is in july##6
8. the fisherman is somewhere to the right of the teacher##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Job         | bartender  | lawyer | teacher    | fisherman |
| Transport   | june | july | march | november  |

