.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, lemonade, cola, tea
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, surfing, swimming, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is golf is not the person drinking coffee##6
2. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
4. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
5. the person drinking cola is not the person who's sport is weightlifting##6
6. the person who's sport is surfing is not the person drinking lemonade##6
7. the person who's sport is weightlifting is in an even position##4
8. the person drinking cola is the person who's sport is golf##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |       2       |    3    |    4     |
| Pet     | cola | coffee        | tea  | lemonade     |
| Sport   | golf     | weightlifting | surfing | swimming |

