2. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the right of the owner of the ferret##5
3. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##3
4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far left##1
5. the owner of the pony is the person who's sport is sailing##1
6. the person who's sport is skateboarding is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##5
7. the person who's sport is skateboarding is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |      2      |       3       |       4       |
